    "body": "**<sub><sub>![P2 Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/P2-yellow?style=flat)</sub></sub>  Bump the TV DB version with the 2026 rows**\n\nBecause this data change leaves `db_version` at the parent value `2026.05.31` while adding 28 models, installed configurators that already bundle the prior 296-row DB will ignore the refreshed docs copy: Step 3 only replaces the local DB when `isNewer(db, remote)` is true, and equal versions return false. In that same-day update scenario, clicking \"Update list\" never exposes the new 2026 rows until a rebuilt app is installed, so this DB expansion should carry a strictly newer version or the comparison needs another monotonic key.\n\nUseful? React with 👍 / 👎.",
